## API 항목명

### API설명

> Shell code : 

```bash
POST /auth/1.0/token HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:38080
Content-Type: application/json
Content-Length: 126

{
    "userKey" : "oAfhQUXpWEGIvlFb7oCka3pozuLA1TNT5NhhTUdUYMDnMo3rng",
    "tenantKey" : "TMS",
    "serviceKey" : "WORKUP"
}
```

> JSON code:

```json
{
    "data": {

        "RSAExponent": "10001",

}
```
